&lt;p>Used in the majority of encounters. Due to phasing, in some instances it may be best to begin with Kasha into Gekko instead.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>
&lt;div class="md__image">
 &lt;img id="[193 111 116 352 94 388]" src="https://www.thebalanceffxiv.com/img/jobs/sam/samurai-opener.jpeg" onclick="openModal(this.id)" alt="" title="Samurai Standard Opener" />
&lt;/div>
&lt;/p>
