&lt;/div>
&lt;/td>
 &lt;td style="text-align: left">Gekko&lt;/td>
 &lt;td style="text-align: left">Single target third step combo. 160 potency. If combo from Jinpu, increases to 370 potency, 420 potency from rear. Combo Bonus: Getsu Sen, +10 Kenki.&lt;/td>
 &lt;/tr>
 &lt;tr>
 &lt;td style="text-align: left">
&lt;div class="md__image">
