&lt;/div>
&lt;/td>
 &lt;td style="text-align: left">Kasha&lt;/td>
 &lt;td style="text-align: left">Single target third step combo. 160 potency. If combo from Shifu, increases to 370 potency, 420 potency from flank. Combo Bonus: Ka Sen, +10 Kenki.&lt;/td>
 &lt;/tr>
 &lt;tr>
 &lt;td style="text-align: left">
&lt;div class="md__image">
 &lt;img id="[217 138 124 448 130 303]" src="https://xivapi.com/i/003000/003166_hr1.png" onclick="openModal(this.id)" alt="Yukikaze" />
&lt;/div>
&lt;/td>
 &lt;td style="text-align: left">Yukikaze&lt;/td>
 &lt;td style="text-align: left">Single target second step combo. 160 potency, 340 potency if combo from Hakaze. Combo Bonus: Setsu Sen, +15 Kenki.&lt;/td>
 &lt;/tr>
 &lt;tr>
 &lt;td style="text-align: left">
&lt;div class="md__image">
 &lt;img id="[111 54 11 75 352 405]" src="https://xivapi.com/i/003000/003155_hr1.png" onclick="openModal(this.id)" alt="Enpi" />
&lt;/div>
&lt;/td>
 &lt;td style="text-align: left">Enpi&lt;/td>
 &lt;td style="text-align: left">Single target ranged attack, 100 potency, 270 if combo (Yaten). +10 Kenki.&lt;/td>
 &lt;/tr>
 &lt;/tbody>
&lt;/table>
